Iranian Foreign Minister Mohammad Javad Zarif tweeted on Sunday that the United States may be &#8220;milking&#8221; Saudi Arabia of $480 billion after Washington signed major deals with Tehran&#8217;s Gulf rival.&#8220;Iran &#8212; fresh from real elections &#8212; attacked by @POTUS in that bastion of democracy &amp; moderation. Foreign Policy or simply milking KSA of $480B?&#8221; Zarif tweeted.It was the first Iranian reaction to US President Donald Trump&#8217;s visit to Saudi Arabia, and comes after Iranian President Hassan Rouhani&#8217;s re-election to a second term.-AFP